thread.title: Southwest Passenger Died of Blunt-Impact Trauma, Officials Say

author: Scott Calvert
title: Southwest Passenger Died of Blunt-Impact Trauma, Officials Say

organizations.name: southwest passenger died of blunt-impact trauma

text:
Blunt-impact trauma caused the death of a passenger on the Southwest AirlinesCo. flight that made an emergency landing Tuesday in Philadelphia after an engine blew apart in midair, officials said Thursday.
Passenger Jennifer Riordan died from blunt-impact trauma to the head, neck and torso, said a spokesman for the Philadelphia Department of Public Health.
